    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This RFC defines a mechanism by which TCP/UDP based clients can access OSI Directory Service without the overhead of the ISO transport and presentation protocols required to implement full-blown DAP.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify any standard.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
